    "description": "Phase1 HTTP API. Import into Postman (File → Import). Set collection variables: baseUrl, client (merchant|customer), campaignId, landingPageId, userId.\n\n---\nEquivalent curl (replace vars):\n\n```bash\nBASE=http://localhost:8080/campaign-center-api/v1\nCLIENT=customer\n```",
